For the quota period from 1 January to 31 December 2000, Annex I to Regulation (EC) No 2505/96 shall be amended as follows:
- order No 09.2799: the amount of the tariff quota shall be altered to 47000 tonnes;
- order No 09.2939: the amount of the tariff quota shall be altered to 260000000 units;
- order No 09.2949: the amount of the tariff quota shall be altered to 16000000 units;
- order No 09.2959: the amount of the tariff quota shall be altered to 80000 tonnes;
- order No 09.2985: the amount of the tariff quota shall be altered to 200000 units.
